  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/business-law/docs/f/11-945rf-future-of-narrative-reporting-consulting-new-framework-form.doc"&gt;The future of narrative reporting: consulting on a new reporting framework. Response form (DOC, 177 Kb)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/business-law/docs/n/11-1293-narrative-reporting-impact-assessment.pdf"&gt;Narrative reporting: impact assessment (PDF, 234 Kb)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/business-law/docs/f/11-1294-future-of-narrative-reporting-regulatory-policy-committee-opinion.pdf"&gt;Regulatory Policy Committee opinion: impact assessment on narrative reporting (PDF, 69 Kb)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
